00535 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
00536 /// Bit 0: stallGuardTM status
00537 /// (1: threshold reached)
00538 /// Bit 1: Overtemperature
00539 /// (1: driver is shut down due to overtemperature)
00540 /// Bit 2: Pre-warning overtemperature
00541 /// (1: Threshold is exceeded)
00542 /// Bit 3: Short to ground A
00543 /// (1: Short condition etected, driver currently shut down)
00544 /// Bit 4: Short to ground B
00545 /// (1: Short condition detected, driver currently shut down)
00546 /// Bit 5: Open load A
00547 /// (1: no chopper event has happened during the last period with constant coil polarity)
00548 /// Bit 6: Open load B
00549 /// (1: no chopper event has happened during the last period with constant coil polarity)
00550 /// Bit 7: Stand still
00551 /// (1: No step impulse occurred on the step input during the last 2^20 clock cycles)
00552 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
